            project providing calculation tools for board games. All game names,
            artwork, and related intellectual property belong to their respective
            publishers. GameKeeper does not reproduce game rules, components, or
            gameplay mechanics. We strongly encourage purchasing games from official
            retailers to support the board game industry.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-muted-foreground mx-auto max-w-3xl text-xs leading-relaxed">
            <strong>Data Attribution:</strong> Game information and ratings provided
            by
            <a
